TextEng: What are you talking about? And why did you attack me?
Text: 무슨 소리야? 그리고 왜 날 공격한 거야?

TextEng: Who are you?
Text: 너 누구야?

TextEng: What you be talking 'bout? Why you attack me?
Text: 무슨 소리 하는 거야? 왜 나 공격했어?

TextEng: Who you be?
Text: 너 누구야?

TextEng: Yes, this is the Wood. Why did you just attack me?
Text: 그래, 여긴 숲이야. 왜 날 공격한 거야?

TextEng: I am asking the questions here. You should have known better than to attack me.
Text: 질문하는 건 나야. 날 공격한 건 잘못된 선택이었어.

TextEng: Yes, this be the Wood. Why you attack me?
Text: 응, 여기 숲이야. 왜 나 공격했어?

TextEng: You no ask questions. You be dumb to attack me.
Text: 너 질문 안 해. 나 공격한 건 멍청한 짓이었어.

TextEng: Don't you remember anything about your captivity?
Text: 포로였던 것에 대해 아무것도 기억 안 나?

TextEng: All right, you should get out of here now.
Text: 알았어, 이제 여기서 나가.

TextEng: You no remember being held?
Text: 너 잡혀 있었던 거 기억 안 나?

TextEng: Okay. You better go now.
Text: 알았어. 이제 가는 게 좋아.

TextEng: I think you are trying to trick me. Die foolish man!
Text: 날 속이려는 것 같은데. 죽어라, 멍청한 놈!

TextEng: You be sneaky. You try to trick me, but now me kill you!
Text: 너 교활해. 나 속이려 하지만 이제 나 너 죽여!

TextEng: Let me ask you some questions about what you knew before you were captured.
Text: 잡히기 전에 알았던 것에 대해 질문 좀 할게.

TextEng: Me want know what you learn before you forgot stuff. You answer me questions.
Text: 나 네가 기억 잃기 전에 알았던 거 알고 싶어. 너 내 질문 답해.

TextEng: What did you discover about what is happening to the animals in the Wood?
Text: 숲의 동물들에게 무슨 일이 일어나고 있는지 뭘 발견했어?

TextEng: There are some druids missing. Do you know what happened to them?
Text: 실종된 드루이드들이 있어. 그들에게 무슨 일이 있었는지 알아?

TextEng: I heard about a witch named Setara. What do you know about her?
Text: 세타라라는 마녀에 대해 들었어. 그녀에 대해 뭘 알아?

TextEng: What you find 'bout animals attacking?
Text: 동물들 공격하는 거에 대해 뭘 알아냈어?

TextEng: There be druids missing. You know 'bout that?
Text: 드루이드들 실종됐어. 너 그거 알아?

TextEng: Setara be the witch of the Wood. You know 'bout her?
Text: 세타라가 숲의 마녀야. 그녀에 대해 알아?
